snippet.title: Breathedge Chapters 2-3 Trailer
snippet.description:
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/738520/Breathedge/
FB: https://www.fb.me/breathedgegame/

Breathedge Chapter 2 and 3. Trailer. Experience the life of a simple guy with simple needs who tries to survive in the depths of the deep space. Explore, build, kick corpses, and poke everything with a chicken.
The release of the two new chapters of Breathedge will be on September 5.

Music: PhaseShifter - Jason Shaw (https://audionautix.com/index.php)
